OL,3,CMore than half plan to spend on
OL,4,CValentine's Day ` survey
OL,6,FMore than half of the public intend to
OL,7,Fspend money on a spouse or partner
OL,8,Fthis Valentine's Day, with men
OL,9,Fmarginally more likely than women to
OL,10,Fmark the occasion, a survey suggests.
OL,12,FJust over a quarter of people (27%)
OL,13,Fintend to take their partner out for a
OL,14,FValentine's Day meal, 19% will send a
OL,15,Fcard, 10% will buy flowers or drinks
OL,16,Fout and 4% are planning a trip away,
OL,17,Fthe poll for the British Retail
OL,18,FConsortium (BRC) found.
