OL,3,CMore than half plan to spend on
OL,4,CValentine's Day ` survey
OL,6,FSome 65% of 18- to 34-year-olds said
OL,7,Fthey would be spending money on their
OL,8,Fsignificant other, compared with 57%
OL,9,Fof 35- to 54-year-olds, dipping to 39%
OL,10,Fof the over 55s.
OL,12,FSome 55% of men are planning to spend
OL,13,Fon the occasion compared with 49% of
OL,14,Fwomen, while those in London are the
OL,15,Fmost likely geographically to spend
OL,16,Fmoney at 64% compared with 39% of
OL,17,Fthose in the South West.
