OL,3,CMore than half plan to spend on
OL,4,CValentine's Day ` survey
OL,6,FKris Hamer, director of insight at the
OL,7,FBRC, said: "Valentine's Day is an
OL,8,Fimportant moment for millions of
OL,9,Fcouples. Whether it's dinner out, or a
OL,10,Fcard and flowers, many lovebirds will
OL,11,Fbe looking to spend a little extra
OL,12,Fthis Friday.
OL,14,F"Retailers, restaurants and bars have
OL,15,Fall been preparing for weeks to make
OL,16,Fsure Valentine's Day is a little extra
OL,17,Fspecial for all their customers.
